          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Excitation cross sections of the first 2+ levels of",
                "Fe-56,Mo-94,Mo-96,Mo-98 isotopes were obtained by TOF",
                "method at neutron energy 1.4 MeV.The energy dependen-",
                "cies of gamma ray yields from deexcitation of these le-",
                "vels were measured with GELI detector.",
                "These relative dependencies were normalized to the",
                "cross section value at 1.4 MeV.",
                "Data of Liskien H.,Paulsen A.//Nucl.Data Tables,1973,",
                "11,N7,p.569-619// on neutron yields at zero degree for",
                "T(p,n) reaction were used to compare neutron fluxes."
              ]
            }
          ],
